JenaDQ

Class APISemDQ

  • java.lang.Object
    • JenaDQ.APISemDQ

  • public class APISemDQ
extends java.lang.Object
    APISemDQ is the main interface between programmer and JenaDQ. It is integrated using a Facade pattern.
    Author:
    Raúl Reguillo Carmona
